Retrives the country name and/or country code for a given IP address. This
CakePHP component is a (simple) wrapper based on MaxMind's GeoIP PHP API
(geoip.inc), and requires a resource file (GeoIP.dat) to work correctly.

Requirements

geoip.inc
GeoIP.dat

Both files can be downloaded from http://www.maxmind.com/app/geolitecountry.

Installation

Place geoip.inc in app/vendors, and GeoIP.dat in app/webroot.

Demo

Copy the supplied geoip_tests_controller.php to your app/controllers, and
access the countryCode, countryName actions; e.g.

http://path/to/CakePHP/geoip_tests/countryCode/67.205.41.208
http://path/to/CakePHP/geoip_tests/countryName/67.205.41.208

Usage

1. Add "Geoip" to your $components array in your controller; e.g.

$components = array("Geoip");

2. In your controller action:

print $this->Geoip->countryCode("67.205.41.208");

Thanks to MaxMind.